{"tid":535848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［支爆撚gg］沈大師料今年港股最低可冧落兩萬點 目前「一股不留」","createTime":"2018-01-21T09:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T10:35:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cca6eb2b3331fd171c078129b9b6dc730f1d96e4","tid":535848,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"港股今年強勢，上周五再破頂，收報32254點。人稱「大師」的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈出席城市論壇後表示，恒指目前水平已接近見頂，料大市今年最低可回落至20000點以下，更透露指自己目前「一股不留」，強積金戶口亦已轉為保本策略。他解釋，港股現時估值偏離合理水平，且投資者情緒高漲，甚至把「負面消息經過演繹化妝之後變為好消息又攞嚟炒」，令市場風險增加，他料隨外圍或收水，大市將失去支持並轉勢。<br />\n<br />\n不過，對於去年已看好的石油股，他認為受惠油價或能再上，仍然看好。<br />\n<br />\n沈振盈續指雖然港股通的北水流入規模有所增加，但認為持貨力度有所減弱，「唔似以前買隻吉利（175）跟住嘭嘭嘭搞你幾個月，而家通常北水嚟炒你幾日之後定係到」。他補充，「地下北水我就覺得走緊多過嚟緊」，加上在內地資金或收緊，料北水不會長遠湧港。<br />\n<br />\n記者：莫亦熙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180121/57735657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57735657&d=3uCXtnqEHcYCu2otEXs5XtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=db7cfe9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57735657&h=57083c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180121/57735657</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3c7cbc82ad3d4faa935954a6e03283d639c221","tid":535848,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca437fb1003c7f461821f1a00424059a18afa2a0","tid":535848,"uid":55847,